I NEED YOUR HELP! 
#HaveAGoodDayChallenge

Uh oh…the stage is SET! The @campoutbeatbattle returns June 24th. Tickets are available at the link in our bio! This is an all ages show, so children are welcome. But…Wait until you hear this judge panel!!! For this event, we wanted to focus more on judges who specialize in the field of synchronization. There are plenty of ways to make a living as a producer. You don’t have to work with the worlds biggest artist (although that is great), you can get some “mailbox money! Our judges have worked with the likes of the #NBA, #NFL, #Redbull, #ABC, #Starz, #HBO, #Showtime, and more! This will be a crazy event…AND…we just added a phenomenal prize courtesy of one of our judges. We will announce it the day of the battle! #Producers, if you missed out, don’t worry! Follow us and stay tuned for our next event! See you all soon…and welcome…to the Camp Out! ⛺️ 🔥⛺️🔥
.
.
